            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                <h2>Initial Release</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Custom Context Menus</strong>: Add scripts to your Finder right-click menu</li>
                    <li><strong>Three Script Types</strong>: Bash, AppleScript, or Automator workflows</li>
                    <li><strong>Smart Filtering</strong>: Scripts appear only for matching file types</li>
                    <li><strong>Categories</strong>: Organize scripts into groups</li>
                    <li><strong>Test Before Save</strong>: Run scripts on real files before committing</li>
                </ul>
                ]]>
